tool_description: Gets all NFT collections that match a given metadata search in +20 networks and including testnets.
title: NFT Explorer

api_list.name: NFTSearch
api_list.description: Get NFTs that match a given metadata search in all widely used networks

required_parameters.name: filter
required_parameters.description:
- To look into the entire metadata set the value to '*global*'. 
- To have a better response time you can look into a specific field like '*name*'

required_parameters.name: offset
required_parameters.description: Pagination index. Default is set to 0

required_parameters.name: chain
required_parameters.description:
The chain to query:
- eth
- bsc
- avalanche
- polygon
- 0x1
- kovan
- avalanche testnet
- bsc testnet
- mumbai
- ropsten
- 0x3
- 0x4
- goerli

{"name":"NIBIRU - The Stoned Ape Revelations","createdBy":"Spaced Painter","yearCreated":"2020","description":"Open your mind fellow primate and allow me to take you on a cosmic journey deep into Myth and the truth of our origin story. 

The Tree Of Life is lush with fruits of sustenance for the body as well as mind and soul. Amongst its treasures is the alien Mycelium brought to Earth by our Reptilian creators from Nibiru - The Anunnaki – who through the introduction of Psilocybin have manipulated our DNA precipitating evolution from earlier apes onto our current human stage of development. 

Veiled by mystery and forgotten history, the fiery rock our creators came from is known across galaxies by many names: Nibiru, Planet 9, Planet X… What I am able to pass on is that The Stoned Ape Revelations enlightened our common ape ancestor on the meaning of life and our origin and destiny by the secrets and perennial Symbolism gifted by The Anunnaki, which was to later be inscribed onto the Sumerian tablets and carried down millennia by Egyptian and other high civilizations – knowledge of the structure of our solar system, the Ouroboros, the Caduceus, DNA strand, the serpent coiled over the mushroom teacher, winged amulets and other mystical teachings that upgraded us with the knowledge of Astronomy, Philosophy, Medicine, Good & Evil.. Transcendence.

But be not blinded by the riches of these magical gifts Spaced Ape! – as in Eden so in this Tree Of Knowledge the Reptilian forces give only on the basis that Knowledge of Good and Evil opens the door to the latter and can ultimately corrupt chimps and humans alike. After all Nibiru, the Nemesis, continuously awaits behind the sun until it arises and yet again crosses it’s track with the Earth’s orbit to extinguish all in it’s path.
So beware… the snakes are always lurking on the trees especially the ones that bear the most enticing fruits… we humans know this all too well. So may Vision and Balance be with you on your trip my friend, because no one comes out of this journey without battling with the ultimate snake: That One WITHIN.

“NIBIRU - The Stoned Ape Revelations” - Cinematic Immersive VR piece by Spaced Painter.

I’ve worked on this piece over the last two months from concept through the various creation stages till mint. I have hand painted this scene in Virtual Reality and then filmed it in VR choreographed to the inspiring track “Nibiru” by Extra Terra.
